# viaDDSdemo1

viaDDSdemo1 is an ViaSat Data Delivery service API allowing consumers to request data collection from various antenna sites around the world.


## Task [/task]

Required attributes:

    - 'id'  Automatically assigned {task_id}
    - 'StartTime'
    - 'StopTime'
    - 'type'    Track, Test, Maintenance
    
Option attributes:
    - 'stationId'   
        

### Create a New Task [POST]

You may create a new task using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a information about the task. 

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "start time": 2016 021 01:27:45
            "stop time":2016 021 01:28:45
            "type": TRACK
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        [
            [Task][]
        ]

### Delete [DELETE]

+ Response 204


## Tasks Collection [/tasks]

A colleciton of all tasks

+ Model (application/json)

    +   Body
    
            {
                "id": {task_id}
                "start time": 2016 021 01:27:45
                "stop time":2016 021 01:28:45
                "type": TRACK
            }

### List All Tasks [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            [Task][]
        ]
+ Response 200 (application/xml)

        [
            <Tasks>
                <Task>
                    <TaskId>{task_id}</TaskId>
                    <URI>http://viaDDSdemp1/tasks/{task_id}</URI>
                </Task>
            </Tasks>
        ]
            
