## Reservation Collection [/reservations_{user_id}]

A colleciton of all reservations for a particular user

+ Parameters
    + user_id (number) - ID of the dds user in the form of an integer

+ Model (application/json)

    +   Body
    
            {
                "id": {user_id}
                "start time": 2016 021 01:27:45
                "stop time":2016 021 01:28:45
            }


